  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bca\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Recovery of explosives from private land in Kilinochchi",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Explosives have been recovered from a private land in Kanakambikaikulam area under Kilinochchi Police Division.",
        "The police were informed by the land owner when these were identified while the land owner was cleaning the land.",
        "The police said that motor cells, magazines and tear gas canisters have been recovered and steps have been taken to safely deactivate them."
      ],
